https://roadmap.sh/devops

1) Learn any language Python/GO/Ruby or Rust 
2) Learn OS (Windows or Linux)
3) Learn Github/Gitlab or bitcucket
4) Networking (Hosting/DNS/Ip Allocation)
5) Container Kubernetes (K8s) or Docker
6) Configuration tools like ansiables, chef, puppet, octopus, Terraform (we will be using only Terraform and ansibles)
7) CI/CD (Jenkins and or Github Actions).
8) Secrate management (Voult or KeyVault)
9) Monitoring (Datadog/Dynatrace/Gafana)
10) Container Orchestration.


